title: Checkmk Site: Backup Job State
agents: linux
catalog: app/cmk
license: GPLv2
distribution: checkmk
description:
 This check checks the status of Checkmk site backup jobs. It
 will raise a {CRIT} state in case the job failed or the next execution of
 the job is overdue.

item:
 The ID of the site followed by the statement {{backup}} joined with the ID of the job.

discovery:
 One service is created for each site and backup job.
